{"tid":1437772,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[教學] 如何在連登加密通訊","createTime":"2019-08-09T15:23:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T04:50:38.000Z","uid":246823,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"011dac77ad4d8238e3b30af420b1fefc6475941a","tid":1437772,"uid":246823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:23:50.000Z","msg":"話說我之前整左一個開源既加密同解密程式 vCipher。<br />\n舊 post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1419027/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1419027/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1434432/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1434432/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n前版本採用比較簡單及原始既 Vigen&egrave;re Cipher 加密法，依家採用進階加密標準 AES 128 bit CTR mode 加密法（多謝五克巴打提供建議 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n如果你之用過舊版本，有啲舊 key, 由於加密法變左，舊 key 唔用得<br />\n請大家按 &quot;Delete Everything&quot; 產曬啲舊 key 同 cipher, 然後 reload 個版面<br />\n＊呢個動作只需在出現更新加密法既情況下執行一次<br />\n<br />\nWeb 版為 opensource，如果發現啲 code 有問題請係度話我知 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n程式代碼：<a href=\"https://github.com/clmaples/vcipher\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fclmaples%2Fvcipher&d=Zo4i0ptUI%2BsV2bg8TrofrCHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=2cf9d904\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/clmaples/vcipher</a><br />\nWeb 版：<a href=\"https://clmaples.github.io/vcipher\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fclmaples.github.io%2Fvcipher&d=Zo4i0ptUI%2BsV2bg8TrofrCHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=ca3d1e68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://clmaples.github.io/vcipher</a><br />\niOS 版：［開發中］<br />\nAndroid 版：［開發中］<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins><div style=\"text-align: center;\">使用方法</div></ins></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">發佈者</span><br />\n首先，作為發佈者，你要 generate 一條 key:<br />\n按 New, 然後命名：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/85ukMGC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F85ukMGC.png&h=13437830&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8bBjhOi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8bBjhOi.png&h=bc9f5d40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n完成後會顯示在主畫面：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aREHZ2v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaREHZ2v.png&h=50a20e2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\nCopy 條 key, 然後用一個安全方法傳送畀你既接收者（注意，條 key 一定不可公開）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V24T6JQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV24T6JQ.png&h=f85a4fea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n按 Encrypt，然後將你既 message 加密，完成後按 &quot;Copy cipher&quot;。<br />\n呢條 cipher text 就係你會係連登上面 post 出黎畀你既受眾<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n3UT6L2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn3UT6L2.png&h=23ca3258&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">接收者</span><br />\n作為接收者，收到條 key 後，請 import 入去 vCipher 度：<br />\n你可以隨意命名，方便自己識別<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bm8qdpJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbm8qdpJ.png&h=b1343951&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n要解密時，請搵出對應既 key, 然後打開。按 Decrypt, 貼上 cipher text，完成後按 OK，即可見到解密後既內容：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wyasrN4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwyasrN4.png&h=abbc170d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hbFDytj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhbFDytj.png&h=a6ffba49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Scenario</span></span><br />\n你有個 tg group, 有班死黨，每日都會傾唔同既野<br />\n咁有日想傾返上個月個議題，但要碌到唔知幾多千條 message 上去，假設個 group 已傾過有 100 個議題，咁已經好亂。雖然可以就每個議題開新 group, 但咁多 group 又係亂<br />\n<br />\n咁所以你可以係 group 入面 share 一條 key，然後係討論區開 post<br />\n可以因應情況將敏既說話加密，然後成個 post 啲加密字符，淨係你地先 decrypt 到<br />\n<br />\n咁你地可以係討論區開無限個議題，可以暫停，隨時返炒討論又得<br />\n<br />\nTIP: 如果連post title 都加密左，放便自已唔洗下下decrypt 個 title, 可以係標題 mark 個 number, 然後係 tg group 寫返個 number 同議題既 title"},{"pid":"86705de695be005b0c84fa9896bbaee73ce2dbf2","tid":1437772,"uid":246823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:26:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">2019年8月9日 更新</span><br />\n- 安全性修正：加上 IV 入加密模式 CRT（多謝五克巴打既提示）<br />\n- 支援用中文命名啲 keys<br />\n- 新增 &quot;Clear&quot; 按鈕，清除單一 key 既相關 message"},{"pid":"9ba53d1261e7de8acc13c4a787ca4f334153f4e6","tid":1437772,"uid":68220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T02:27:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a1bc79d3f7878f8ee84793ff7bc05ae8878a2ea1","tid":1437772,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T02:43:00.000Z","msg":"點解唔用 DES?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c686614a5f1e6d4529a823f37b8d9ff0826391dc","tid":1437772,"uid":246823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1bc79d3f7878f8ee84793ff7bc05ae8878a2ea1","tid":1437772,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T02:43:00.000Z","msg":"點解唔用 DES?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:47:57.000Z","msg":"好似係因為 DES encrypt 唔到太多 data<br />\n同埋 AES 係 Advanced Encryption Standard"},{"pid":"06cd2708d7b37361007628b7a55b8c706aa2a431","tid":1437772,"uid":172627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:48:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90da871cfc5502d1316966b4ee86aa495ab9e808","tid":1437772,"uid":272529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:51:06.000Z","msg":"(和理非全面升級)星期五，日0消費！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1436038\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1436038</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\nBye Buy Day 特別活動第一彈！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1427160\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1427160</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HBuQUvK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHBuQUvK.png&h=2ab8ac09&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bfcad6bef137d0ff50a58f166ac519a14a5da7fe","tid":1437772,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:54:11.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f377bd34bb12df8b3ec647e1a72d1d96fa21fa1d","tid":1437772,"uid":246823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:54:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">更新：2019年8月10日 11:50</span><br />\n- 新增 RSA 加密法，key size 512 bit，用 public key 加密，private key 解密<br />\n- 更新介面，放便係 AES 同 RSA 之間轉換，預設為 RSA"},{"pid":"5349f526f263fd790e8a1d3d975f3da02dd993a1","tid":1437772,"uid":246823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:18:39.000Z","msg":"另外有字眼上更改，因為唔夠位，&quot;Delete Everything&quot; 改為 &quot;Reset&quot;"},{"pid":"c2c68a1709ba06e4874ca5922ecf0de0a9d4198d","tid":1437772,"uid":246823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:26:48.000Z","msg":"我既 public key<br />\n<br />\n-----BEGIN PUBLIC KEY-----MFwwDQYJKoZIhvcNAQEBBQADSwAwSAJBALwgS8PjMyyqetcdAelBJ8RbN8aIhZGLUq7BJJgOKsfx29qMyurNPDKAXqpqAG02mmDI0xJUP5SeLs/PobCCKwUCAwEAAQ==-----END PUBLIC KEY-----<br />\n<br />\n有興趣加我 tg 既可以用條呢 key 加密你地既 <a href=\"https://t.me/xxxxxxxx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fxxxxxxxx&d=Zo4i0ptUI%2BsV2bg8TrofrCHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=51fdb6c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/xxxxxxxx</a> 然後 post 係度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdac97e516bdb49f3c0d1f7d4852ddb54ba0cee3","tid":1437772,"uid":246823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:49:16.000Z","msg":"點解要分 RSA 同 AES ?<br />\n<br />\n簡單黎講，RSA 會 gen 兩條 key: public key 同 private key<br />\npublic key 用黎加密，你可以畀條 key 公開出去<br />\nprivate key 用黎解密，你自己 keep 住，要絕對保密<br />\n咁樣你就係唯一擁有條 private key 既人<br />\n注意，RSA 一般用黎加密較細既 information，例如一個網址，一句說話<br />\n<br />\n而 AES 只係得一條 key, 同時用黎加密同解密，只可以 share 畀信得過既人。AES 可以用黎加密較大既 data，例如檔案，文件等等<br />\n<br />\n所以要係連登呢啲公眾場合放條 key 出黎既話，一定係 generate 一對 RSA keys, 然後放條 public key 出黎<br />\n<br />\n其中一種情況係：<br />\nA 畀條 RSA public key 畀 B<br />\nB gen 一條 AES key, 再用 A 既 public key 加密<br />\n將得出既密符 post 出黎畀 A<br />\nA 用佢既 RSA private key 解密，得出 B 既 AES key<br />\n咁之後 A 同 B 都可以用同一條 AES key 係討論區傾秘密野"},{"pid":"5a01af8ca3a4752af4327da503b212705e0eb925","tid":1437772,"uid":280786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"011dac77ad4d8238e3b30af420b1fefc6475941a","tid":1437772,"uid":246823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:23:50.000Z","msg":"話說我之前整左一個開源既加密同解密程式 vCipher。<br />\n舊 post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1419027/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1419027/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1434432/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1434432/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n前版本採用比較簡單及原始既 Vigen&egrave;re Cipher 加密法，依家採用進階加密標準 AES 128 bit CTR mode 加密法（多謝五克巴打提供建議 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n如果你之用過舊版本，有啲舊 key, 由於加密法變左，舊 key 唔用得<br />\n請大家按 &quot;Delete Everything&quot; 產曬啲舊 key 同 cipher, 然後 reload 個版面<br />\n＊呢個動作只需在出現更新加密法既情況下執行一次<br />\n<br />\nWeb 版為 opensource，如果發現啲 code 有問題請係度話我知 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n程式代碼：<a href=\"https://github.com/clmaples/vcipher\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fclmaples%2Fvcipher&d=Zo4i0ptUI%2BsV2bg8TrofrCHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=2cf9d904\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/clmaples/vcipher</a><br />\nWeb 版：<a href=\"https://clmaples.github.io/vcipher\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fclmaples.github.io%2Fvcipher&d=Zo4i0ptUI%2BsV2bg8TrofrCHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=ca3d1e68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://clmaples.github.io/vcipher</a><br />\niOS 版：［開發中］<br />\nAndroid 版：［開發中］<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins><div style=\"text-align: center;\">使用方法</div></ins></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">發佈者</span><br />\n首先，作為發佈者，你要 generate 一條 key:<br />\n按 New, 然後命名：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/85ukMGC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F85ukMGC.png&h=13437830&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8bBjhOi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8bBjhOi.png&h=bc9f5d40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n完成後會顯示在主畫面：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aREHZ2v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaREHZ2v.png&h=50a20e2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\nCopy 條 key, 然後用一個安全方法傳送畀你既接收者（注意，條 key 一定不可公開）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V24T6JQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV24T6JQ.png&h=f85a4fea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n按 Encrypt，然後將你既 message 加密，完成後按 &quot;Copy cipher&quot;。<br />\n呢條 cipher text 就係你會係連登上面 post 出黎畀你既受眾<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n3UT6L2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn3UT6L2.png&h=23ca3258&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">接收者</span><br />\n作為接收者，收到條 key 後，請 import 入去 vCipher 度：<br />\n你可以隨意命名，方便自己識別<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bm8qdpJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbm8qdpJ.png&h=b1343951&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n要解密時，請搵出對應既 key, 然後打開。按 Decrypt, 貼上 cipher text，完成後按 OK，即可見到解密後既內容：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wyasrN4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwyasrN4.png&h=abbc170d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hbFDytj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhbFDytj.png&h=a6ffba49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Scenario</span></span><br />\n你有個 tg group, 有班死黨，每日都會傾唔同既野<br />\n咁有日想傾返上個月個議題，但要碌到唔知幾多千條 message 上去，假設個 group 已傾過有 100 個議題，咁已經好亂。雖然可以就每個議題開新 group, 但咁多 group 又係亂<br />\n<br />\n咁所以你可以係 group 入面 share 一條 key，然後係討論區開 post<br />\n可以因應情況將敏既說話加密，然後成個 post 啲加密字符，淨係你地先 decrypt 到<br />\n<br />\n咁你地可以係討論區開無限個議題，可以暫停，隨時返炒討論又得<br />\n<br />\nTIP: 如果連post title 都加密左，放便自已唔洗下下decrypt 個 title, 可以係標題 mark 個 number, 然後係 tg group 寫返個 number 同議題既 title"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T04:50:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"}]}